{"tid":2308044,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"買紅酒挺澳洲！多國議員聲援抵抗中國霸凌：不向強權屈服","createTime":"2020-12-01T14:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T14:49:11.000Z","uid":291835,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2e62ec1cd8a0161a206a53aae19c7b3f28abd5c8","tid":2308044,"uid":291835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T14:45:14.000Z","msg":"中國近來對澳洲祭出連串關稅報復，數日前對澳洲葡萄酒課徵鉅額反傾銷稅，引發國際力挺澳洲葡萄酒的聲浪。來自紐西蘭、德國、英國、義大利、美國、挪威、日本、斯洛伐克、瑞典和丹麥等多國議員，今齊聲透過影片發起「12月買紅酒挺澳洲」活動，希望透過支持澳洲葡萄酒，「讓中國共產黨知道，我們不會向強權屈服！乾杯！」我駐美代表蕭美琴也在推特上轉發該影片並幽默說，「似乎是時候囤幾瓶澳洲葡萄酒了」。..........<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3368301\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3368301&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2QKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=d81da4c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3368301&h=1b7a305c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3368301</a>"},{"pid":"ad23942fe2a7a63dee3ae699bdb6a3a60a718aa9","tid":2308044,"uid":88133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T14:45:59.000Z","msg":"反共經濟圈"},{"pid":"5d9308c0de1d16a6ae6286dfbe770144cd55e246","tid":2308044,"uid":291835,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T14:47:46.000Z","msg":"唔計英國, 澳洲係惡法後第一個出來收香港人既國家.<br />\n<br />\n大家唔飲酒都搵其他野支持下"},{"pid":"77ac8f9f423f3fc2379fd192485458bcaca2d2a8","tid":2308044,"uid":291835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T15:02:35.000Z","msg":"有無人知雙羊牌米係咪真係澳洲出? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n米長期要食."},{"pid":"418c670d9fd124e01eba2bf23d88303f4fef5b2f","tid":2308044,"uid":119667,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T15:02:44.000Z","msg":"少飲酒都落街買左支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ewHW7gT.png\" data-th